   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"To my lord brother Makarios, Isidoros, greetings. Since you noted that Demetrios has given to me for Aion 750 myriads denarii in silver, hand over to Aion the other 300 myriads of denarii in silver. But do not neglect it, my lord brother. I pray for your good health."</ab>
